Adidas Plans Two-Digit Revenue Growth in Russia, dpa-AFX Says

-- B y   J u l i e   C r u z
-- 
2011-10-10T05:42:51Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-10/adidas-plans-two-digit-revenue-growth-in-russia-dpa-afx-says.html
Adidas AG plans to increase revenue
in  Russia  and the  Commonwealth of Independent States  by two
digits on average per year until 2015, dpa-AFX reported, citing
an investor conference in Moscow.  Adidas wants to increase revenue to above 1 billion euros
($1.4 billion) by 2013, at comparable exchange rates, dpa-AFX
said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Julie Cruz in Frankfurt at 
